</div>
<br />
▼我们从花莲、青岛、贵阳、无锡、崇明这些行业内并不拔尖的地区，选择各自可圈可点的部分带来的分享，同样精彩。<br />
<br />
<div class="aw-upload-img-list active">
	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161118/3901ecfe8993d2827c07d543b71dbf66.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161118/3901ecfe8993d2827c07d543b71dbf66.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="10.jpg" alt="10.jpg" /></a>
</div>
