<div class="aw-upload-img-list active">
	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161118/5c63efe594c4d481ade6e503dff3de14.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161118/5c63efe594c4d481ade6e503dff3de14.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="11.jpg" alt="11.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<br />
▼这是行业内目前热议的话题，我们勇敢的拿到桌面上摊开来。引起了广泛的大讨论，其中几何民宿的陈宫平成为众人追捧的对象。<br />
<br />
<div class="aw-upload-img-list active">
	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161118/2743d5a0557ce6f84052703d4ba8b04c.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161118/2743d5a0557ce6f84052703d4ba8b04c.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="12.jpg" alt="12.jpg" /></a>
</div>
