<div class="aw-upload-img-list active">
	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161118/0c2ba667fbd3ecc6f7c12e8a9903605e.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161118/0c2ba667fbd3ecc6f7c12e8a9903605e.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="13.jpg" alt="13.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<br />
▼来自台湾民宿业背后真正的推手，为大家全面解读了台湾民宿行业标准的行涉之路，再度将全场气氛引爆。<br />
<br />
<div class="aw-upload-img-list active">
	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161118/0d311390b761c24aff55ed13b282e44b.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161118/0d311390b761c24aff55ed13b282e44b.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="14.jpg" alt="14.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<br />
▼多年从事民宿及文创产业，并对民宿问题有颇多思考与见解的夏昱贤先生，将他多年的所思所感娓娓道来，也将与会来宾带入思考路径。<br />
<br />
