				<div class="pull-right hidden-xs contribute">
			<span class="pull-right text-color-999">贡献</span>
		    		    <a class="aw-user-name" data-id="1" href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/?/people/iHots" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/avatar/000/00/00/01_avatar_mid.jpg" alt="" /></a>
