<br />
<div class="aw-upload-img-list active">
	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161108/70b97f855529e14dfa66627403454dbf.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161108/70b97f855529e14dfa66627403454dbf.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="6.jpg" alt="6.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<br />
<div class="aw-upload-img-list active">
	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161108/08f8f56ebb141213b1997200e071c83c.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161108/08f8f56ebb141213b1997200e071c83c.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="7.jpg" alt="7.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<br />
<div class="aw-upload-img-list active">
	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161108/19dea96e62ecf145facdb0e3dda9bcd0.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161108/19dea96e62ecf145facdb0e3dda9bcd0.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="8.jpg" alt="8.jpg" /></a>
</div>
