 <br />
<div class="aw-upload-img-list active">
	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161108/c7202e07239f8580ade6b5e95e6d6412.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161108/c7202e07239f8580ade6b5e95e6d6412.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="5.jpg" alt="5.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<br />
