	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161103/bd398041765a1231a269d3d4840d556e.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161103/bd398041765a1231a269d3d4840d556e.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="古院2.jpg" alt="古院2.jpg" /></a>
