<br />
<div class="aw-upload-img-list active">
	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161103/f169a99af68f35d04b11096b4f133c93.jpg" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161103/f169a99af68f35d04b11096b4f133c93.jpg" class="img-polaroid" title="safe-travel.jpg" alt="safe-travel.jpg" /></a>
</div>
