	<a href="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161103/1412f68ef85a212da19e0d4d0ea77148.png" target="_blank" data-fancybox-group="thumb" rel="lightbox"><img src="http://www.hotelbrain.cn/uploads/article/20161103/1412f68ef85a212da19e0d4d0ea77148.png" class="img-polaroid" title="无标题.png" alt="无标题.png" /></a>
